I love puzzles, so the more the merrier. A rebus is just another puzzle within the puzzle, like words that link in patterns or contain other words inside of themselves. For me, these multi-layered designs are more fun than the average themeless puzzle, and that ‚Äúaha‚Äù moment when the coin drops into my brain slot is still addictive.

